{"word":"αἰτίζω","slug":"αἰτίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>αἰτίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>epic form of <a href='S:αἰτέω'><el>αἰτέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to ask, beg</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <el>σῖτον</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to beg of</i>, <el>μνηστῆρας</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>αἰτίζων βόσκειν ἣν γαστέρα</el> to fill one's belly <i>by begging</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}